data.title: 2017 Ain't Nothing You Can Do
data.meta_description: John Primer & Bob Corritore are back with this brilliant follow-up to their critically acclaimed 2013 Delta Groove debut "Knockin' Around These Blues". Sit back and enjoy "Ain't Nothing You Can Do" backed up by an ALL-STAR BAND: Legendary Henry Gray, Barrelhouse Chuck, Big Jon Atkinson, Troy Sandow, Chris James, Patrick Rynn and Brian Fahey. SONGS 1) POOR MAN BLUES 2) ELEVATE ME MAMA 3) HOLD ME IN YOUR ARMS 4) BIG LEG WOMAN 5) GAMBLING BLUES 6) HARMONICA BOOGALOO 7) AIN'T NOTHING YOU CAN DO 8) FOR THE LOVE OF A WOMAN 9) MAY I HAVE A TALK WITH YOU 10) WHEN I LEAVE HOME
data.text:
John Primer & Bob Corritore are back with this brilliant follow-up to their critically acclaimed 2013 Delta Groove debut "Knockin' Around These Blues". Sit back and enjoy "Ain't Nothing You Can Do" backed up by an ALL-STAR BAND: Legendary Henry Gray, Barrelhouse Chuck, Big Jon Atkinson, Troy Sandow, Chris James, Patrick Rynn and Brian Fahey.
